<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ</title>
    <link href="/css/faq.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1 class="faq-title">FAQ</h1><br>
        
        <div class="faq-list">
            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary class="faq-question">Do you offer custom cakes?</summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes! We specialize in custom cakes for all occasions. Contact us for more details.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary class="faq-question">How far in advance should I place an order?</summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">We recommend placing your order at least 3 days in advance for standard cakes and 1 week for custom designs.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary class="faq-question">Do you have vegan or gluten-free options?</summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer both vegan and gluten-free cakes. Please inform us of any dietary restrictions.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-item">
                <summary class="faq-question">Do you deliver?</summary>
                <p class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer delivery within a 10-mile radius. Additional charges may apply.</p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
